sequenceDiagram
  participant Detector as Incident Detector
  participant Metrics as Metrics Provider
  participant Logs as Log Provider
  participant Traces as Trace Provider
  participant JFR as JFR Provider
  participant Store as Evidence Store
  participant GUI as JavaFX GUI
  participant MCP as MCP Server

  Detector->>Metrics: Evaluate thresholds
  Detector->>Store: Create incident
  Detector->>Logs: Collect T-5m to T+5m logs
  Detector->>Traces: Collect related traces
  Detector->>JFR: Dump or index JFR snapshot
  Logs->>Store: Store evidence references
  Traces->>Store: Store evidence references
  JFR->>Store: Store JFR artifact reference
  GUI->>Store: Load incident detail
  MCP->>Store: Query read-only evidence
